      "post_content": "I love that there is a story that ties the cards in each set together. Magic the Gathering is awesome I love it. Awesome card game that requires strategizing, problem-solving, thinking outside of the box, designing and executing! And it has an awesome story that gives a background to all the cards? Just amazing. Such a rich fantasy world. Well done wizards, well done.",
